<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Under Maintenance | DR Preeti Global University</title>

  <style>
    *{
      margin:0;
      padding:0;
      box-sizing:border-box;
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
    }

    body{
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a, #1e293b);
      color:#fff;
      height:100vh;
      display:flex;
      justify-content:center;
      align-items:center;
      text-align:center;
      padding:20px;
    }

    .container{
      max-width:700px;
      width:100%;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      padding:50px 35px;
      border-radius:20px;
      box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    }

    .logo{
      font-size:28px;
      font-weight:bold;
      color:#38bdf8;
      margin-bottom:15px;
      letter-spacing:1px;
    }

    h1{
      font-size:42px;
      margin-bottom:20px;
    }

    p{
      font-size:18px;
      line-height:1.7;
      color:#cbd5e1;
      margin-bottom:30px;
    }

    .status{
      display:inline-block;
      padding:12px 25px;
      background:#38bdf8;
      color:#0f172a;
      font-weight:bold;
      border-radius:50px;
      font-size:15px;
    }

    .footer{
      margin-top:35px;
      font-size:14px;
      color:#94a3b8;
    }

    @media(max-width:768px){
      h1{
        font-size:32px;
      }

      p{
        font-size:16px;
      }

      .container{
        padding:40px 25px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="container">
    
    <div class="logo">
      DR PREETI GLOBAL UNIVERSITY
    </div>

    <h1>Website Under Maintenance</h1>

    <p>
      We are currently upgrading our website to improve your experience.
      Our team is working hard to bring everything back online as soon as possible.
    </p>

    <div class="status">
      We'll Be Back Soon
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      © 2026 DR Preeti Global University. All Rights Reserved.
    </div>

  </div>

</body>
</html>